Rename the `CreationTab` type to `CreationMode` and the `initialTab` field to `initialMode` in the agent-creation Zustand store, keeping backward-compatible deprecated aliases.

## Files to modify

### `apps/client/src/layers/shared/model/agent-creation-store.ts`

Replace the entire file contents with:

```typescript
import { create } from 'zustand';

export type CreationMode = 'new' | 'template' | 'import';

/** @deprecated Use CreationMode instead */
export type CreationTab = CreationMode;

interface AgentCreationState {
  isOpen: boolean;
  initialMode: CreationMode;
  open: (mode?: CreationMode) => void;
  close: () => void;
}

/** Global dialog state for the Create Agent dialog. */
export const useAgentCreationStore = create<AgentCreationState>((set) => ({
  isOpen: false,
  initialMode: 'new',
  open: (mode?: CreationMode) => set({ isOpen: true, initialMode: mode ?? 'new' }),
  close: () => set({ isOpen: false, initialMode: 'new' }),
}));
```

Key changes:
- `CreationTab` type renamed to `CreationMode` (same union: `'new' | 'template' | 'import'`)
- `CreationTab` kept as a deprecated type alias pointing to `CreationMode`
- `initialTab` field renamed to `initialMode`
- `open(tab?)` parameter renamed to `open(mode?)` — same signature, same string literals
- All existing callers (`AddAgentMenu`, `SidebarTabRow`, `AgentsHeader`, command palette) pass the same string literals and continue working without changes

